name: Point Cloud Brazil
description: A cloud of points containing hidden images from around Brazil. Enter a code to resize the points and if correct you will see the shape of one of Brazil's wonders. The shapes are traced from photos I made myself. Try these codes to see how it works: 0147241273, 5240292836 and 1212731666. There are 3 more hidden shapes and I will provide the codes to buyers after proof of purchase.
